tangle fern
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:<i>Gleichenia dicarpa</i> (formerly <i>alpina, circinata</i>), having thin, spidery pinnae.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
